text: Géza Bejek (born 20 April 1934) is a Hungarian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1934 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Hungary Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Székesfehérvár
